00:54:20,959 --> 00:54:22,550
Why didn't you say anything?

785
00:54:22,718 --> 00:54:23,926
I only learned it today.

786
00:54:24,534 --> 00:54:25,553
I'm not sure

787
00:54:25,721 --> 00:54:27,071
