789
00:54:28,984 --> 00:54:31,309
Perhaps it's because
I had drunk so much of your blood.

790
00:54:36,662 --> 00:54:38,162
I know what you are.

791
00:54:44,703 --> 00:54:46,853
We're heading to the airport now.

792
00:54:47,846 --> 00:54:49,533
I've got the speech here.

793
00:54:49,658 --> 00:54:52,291
I'll have it all memorized
by the time we land in Oregon.

794
00:54:53,784 --> 00:54:55,484
No, go ahead. I'll hold.

795
00:55:14,407 --> 00:55:15,394
Miss Flanagan.

796
00:55:16,615 --> 00:55:19,293
<i>Recapping the top stories this evening,
