of the country remains undecided.

802
00:55:39,628 --> 00:55:41,285
<i>Does that help you decide, America?</i>

803
00:55:41,637 --> 00:55:43,487
<i>Do not turn off the camera!</i>

804
00:55:45,386 --> 00:55:47,206
<i>You've seen how quickly I can kill.</i>

805
00:55:53,640 --> 00:55:55,142
Ladies and gentlemen...

806
00:55:55,575 --> 00:55:56,575
my name...

