812
00:56:10,572 --> 00:56:13,796
and I suppose
in a few small ways we are.

813
00:56:13,921 --> 00:56:15,079
We're narcissists.

814
00:56:15,764 --> 00:56:17,823
<i>We care only about
getting what we want,</i>

815
00:56:17,948 --> 00:56:20,398
<i>no matter what the cost,
just like you.</i>

816
00:56:20,573 --> 00:56:21,998
<i>Global warming,</i>

817
00:56:22,212 --> 00:56:24,062
<i>perpetual war, toxic waste,</i>

818
00:56:24,199 --> 00:56:27,928
<i>child labor, torture, genocide.</i>
