and your flat-screen TVs,

820
00:56:31,011 --> 00:56:33,777
your blood diamonds,
your designer jeans,

821
00:56:33,902 --> 00:56:36,934
your absurd, garish McMansions!

822
00:56:37,950 --> 00:56:41,104
<i>Futile symbols of permanence
to quell your...</i>

823
00:56:41,951 --> 00:56:42,951
quivering,

824
00:56:43,496 --> 00:56:45,958
spineless souls.

825
00:56:50,639 --> 00:56:51,639
But no.

826
00:56:52,358 --> 00:56:53,408
In the end,

827
00:56:54,363 --> 00:56:56,396
we are...

828
00:56:57,109 --> 00:56:58,926
nothing like you.

829
00:56:59,138 --> 00:57:00,399
We are...

830
00:57:03,161 --> 00:57:04,325
immortal.

831
00:57:05,198 --> 00:57:07,298
Because we drink the true blood,

832
00:57:07,760 --> 00:57:10,260
blood that is living,
organic and human.

833
00:57:14,324 --> 00:57:16,231
<i>And that is the truth</i>

834
00:57:16,356 --> 00:57:18,894
