835
00:57:19,436 --> 00:57:22,225
Because let's face it, eating people
is a tough sell these days.

836
00:57:22,350 --> 00:57:26,764
So they put on their friendly faces
to pass their beloved VRA,

837
00:57:26,889 --> 00:57:28,174
but make no mistake,

838
00:57:28,299 --> 00:57:32,275
mine is the true face of vampires!

839
00:57:38,916 --> 00:57:39,916
Why...

840
00:57:40,991 --> 00:57:43,179
would we seek...

841
00:57:44,071 --> 00:57:45,911
equal rights?

842
00:57:47,744 --> 00:57:48,824
You...

843
00:57:49,697 --> 00:57:52,467
are not our equals.

844
00:57:54,198 --> 00:57:55,598
We will eat you...

845
00:57:56,799 --> 00:57:58,931
